    <processinfo encodinganalog="583">
      <p>The actions of the original processor are unknown. The collection was
		  slightly reorganized and re-described in 1998. The collection includes a series
		  for clippings; however, clippings mentioned within correspondence are filed
		  with the letter in which they are mentioned. Most of the collection was in fair
		  condition though some brittle pages were placed between acid-free sheets.</p>
    </processinfo>
